    <lb n="5"/>ἀλλὰ καὶ πολλοῖς, <choice><corr>ἐπ<supplied reason="lost">ισ</supplied>τάμεναι</corr><sic>επ<supplied reason="lost">ισ</supplied>ταμενοι</sic></choice> <unclear reason="undefined">ὅ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined">ι</unclear> ὐδ<unclear reason="undefined">ὲν</unclear> 

